      "label": "API Domain",
      "description": "Your Zoho API domain based on data center (e.g., www.zohoapis.com for US, www.zohoapis.eu for EU, www.zohoapis.in for India, www.zohoapis.com.au for Australia, www.zohoapis.jp for Japan, www.zohoapis.com.cn for China)",
